    ║         ScriptCapture - LocalScript Monitor          ║
    ║   Detects LocalScript execution and captures code    ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    PLACE THIS SCRIPT INSIDE:
      StarterPlayerScripts  (runs once on client join)
    OR
      StarterCharacterScripts (runs each respawn)

    FEATURES:
      • Detects LocalScripts executed by the local player
